==Tailoring==
A Taro Root can be used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the dyeable [[Tailoring|Shirt And Belt]].  [[File:Shirt159.png|24px]] It can be used in [[dyeing]], serving as an orange dye at the dye pots, located in [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].

==Quests==
*[[Caroline]] may request 100 Taro Roots in the [[Quests#List of Special Orders|"Island Ingredients"]] Special Order. The reward is gold equivalent to 50% of base crop price and the [[Solar Panel]] recipe.

==Trivia==
After harvesting a Taro Root, the ground underneath it will remain watered for the rest of the day.

